{"tid":1476240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我一向都覺得乜野都講求fact check嘅人其實好on9","createTime":"2019-08-15T18:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:50:49.000Z","uid":33909,"like":12,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28a06af5734648c20f0539d6c943a0e8ec168d36","tid":1476240,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"亦都係點解你地永遠都做唔到不割席嘅理由<br />\n因為你地太理性<br />\n下下追求事實<br />\n而對家就唔理三七廿一，總之有乜就信乜，甚至肯去作故仔去撐自己友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話fact check唔岩，而係我覺得呢啲緊急時勢，等你fact check得黎個風已經吹去第二邊<br />\n<br />\n就好似女義士比popo全裸搜身個單，個個出黎話fact check咗先再講<br />\n比你fact check到又點，又有另一單爆起去冚呢一單，到時唔通你地又慢慢fact check?<br />\n<br />\n換過角度睇有冇諗過如果單野係真嘅，當時人會點諗？<br />\n<br />\n所以永遠做唔到對家嘅永不割席只撐隊友嘅原因係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太過有分折能力，下下追求真相</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要記住當對家都係靠fake news去吸更多支持者個陣，你地真係冇必要下下都等真相浮上水面先做文宣，冇必要永遠都我地在明，對家在暗<br />\n咁樣做長遠落去打輿論戰未必有利<br />\n<br />\n因為冇腦嘅就算fake news都照信，有腦嘅一早選擇咗自己應該企邊到"},{"pid":"c599d2600e87a55dc66fd2953d676ccc623404d8","tid":1476240,"uid":33909,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"我知道呢啲說話係唔係幾岩聽<br />\n但有時為達成目的係要不選手段"},{"pid":"c30f7656cf0cf2b1f6de6f2051d68aef635b2cfe","tid":1476240,"uid":30506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33537f4d656082fe2971b13474c7ee629adc556b","tid":1476240,"uid":273234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"對家做法就係 一個大話講得夠多 就變咗一件真嘅事 <br />\n同時嗰班人就會失去左判別真相嘅能力 慢慢就咩都信變成宣傳機器<br />\n<br />\n哨兵嘅嘢就一定要Fact Check <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSyrwOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSyrwOB.jpg&h=8ed4e48b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBgTWfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBgTWfh.jpg&h=a898d1cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c2bfe17b9917618688bdf8cfd7788684c9d58ff","tid":1476240,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c30f7656cf0cf2b1f6de6f2051d68aef635b2cfe","tid":1476240,"uid":30506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"唔係話所有野唔追求FC<br />\n而係對於己方有利嘅contents點解唔好好利用"},{"pid":"0dedf7a3018387603ac044e6f80cd84774b30e03","tid":1476240,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"手動負皮比標題<br />\nFACT CHECK係必須 樓主諗多左"},{"pid":"b4337c066d66df64cb664d7cc1ebfec09113d1e4","tid":1476240,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dedf7a3018387603ac044e6f80cd84774b30e03","tid":1476240,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"手動負皮比標題<br />\nFACT CHECK係必須 樓主諗多左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"FC唔係唔好，但風頭火勢未必係必須"},{"pid":"9d2de639df8e69a16e66c81c849dd6c81b019e2e","tid":1476240,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"有啲道理既<br />\n同勇武同和理既關係有啲似<br />\n但如果有啲明知fake都去狂推又好似同對家無分別<br />\n正/負評揀唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f47ef233b54a941c49616e3b248f4d2adc0420","tid":1476240,"uid":271539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4337c066d66df64cb664d7cc1ebfec09113d1e4","tid":1476240,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dedf7a3018387603ac044e6f80cd84774b30e03","tid":1476240,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"手動負皮比標題<br />\nFACT CHECK係必須 樓主諗多左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"FC唔係唔好，但風頭火勢未必係必須"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:26:34.000Z","msg":"有啲野, 明知係政治宣傳, FC係多尻餘, 只係倒自己米<br />\n比如隔離個